               <msContents>
                  <summary>Images, መልክአ፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                    <locus from = "1r" to = "140r"/>
                    <title type="complete" ref="LIT1850Malkea"/>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                    <locus from = "1r" to = "14v"/>
                    <locus from ="#95r" to = "#95v"/>
                    <title type = "complete" ref = "LIT3007RepCh287"/>
                    <note>The beginning (<locus target = "#1r"/>) is illegible</note>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2"><locus from = "15r" to = "19r"/><title type = "complete" ref = "LIT2915RepCh196"/>
                  <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                    ሰላም፡ ለፅንሰትከ፡ መሠረተ፡ በገር፡ ወውጣኔ። ወለልደትከ፡ ሰላም፡ በብስራተ፡ መልአክ፡ ሠናየ፡ ቅኔ።
                  </incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3"><locus from = "19r" to = "25v"/><title type = "complete" ref = "LIT2999RepCh279"/>
                  <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                    በስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ እሳት፡ በሐቅለ፡ ሕሊና፡ ነዳዲ። ወበስመ፡ ማርያም፡ ድንግል፡ መጥበቢተ፡ ዓለም፡ አባዲ።
                  </incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4"><locus from = "26r" to = "33r"/><title type = "complete" ref="LIT4131Salam"/></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5"><locus from = "33v" to = "34r"/> <title>Greeting to Abib</title>
                  <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                    ሰላም፡ ለከ፡ አቢብ፡ ኅሩይ፡ ዘተከለልከ፡ ሞገስ። እስመ፡ ምስለ፡ ዐቢይ፡ ንጉሥ፡ ዐረይከ፡ ነጊሠ።
                  </incipit>
                  </msItem>
                <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.6"><locus from = "35r" to = "38r"/><title type = "complete" ref = "LIT2940RepCh221"/></msItem>
                <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.7"><locus from = "38r" to = "44r"/><title type = "complete" ref = "LIT2733RepCh17"/>
                  <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                    መኅበረ፡ ምእመናን፡ ወምእምናት፡ እለ፡ ኪያከ፡ ተአመኑ። ለነሢአ፡ ሥጋከ፡ ወትረ፡ ኀበ፡ ተዓየኑ።
                  </incipit>
                  </msItem>
                <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.8"><locus from = "44r" to = "57v"/><title type = "complete" ref = "LIT3082RepCh362"/>
                  <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                    እግዚአብሔር፡ ወሀቤ፡ ብርሃን፡ ዘይሤልሰ፡ በአካሉ። እንዘ፡ ተዋህዶ፡ ያጸንዕ፡ በመለኮቱ፡ ወኃይሉ።
                  </incipit>
                  </msItem>
                <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.9"><locus from = "57v" to = "60v"/>
                  <note>Sälam of the Dərsanä Mika'el, copied for <foreign xml:lang = "gez">አቅባ፡ ሚካኤል፡</foreign><locus target = "#60v"/></note>
                  <title type = "complete" ref = "LIT1295Dersan"/></msItem>
                <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.10"><locus from = "61v" to = "75v"/><title type = "complete" ref = "LIT1860Malkea"/>
                  </msItem>
                <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.11"><locus from = "76r" to = "80r"/><title type = "complete" ref = "LIT2908RepCh189"/>
                <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                  ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምክሙ፡ ዘእምቅድመ፡ ዓለም፡ ህልው። ለር፤እስክሙ፡ ሰላም፡ ወስእርትክሙ፡ ፅእድው።
                </incipit>
              </msItem>
                <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.12"><locus from = "80r" to = "91v"/>
                <title>Image of Mäzra'tä Krəstos, <foreign xml:lang = "gez">መልክዐ፡ መዝራዕተ፡ ክርስቶስ፡</foreign></title>
                <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                  ይትባረክ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ዘአምጽአ፡ ዓለማተ። መዝራዕተ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ያሬድ፡ እንዘ፡ ትብል፡ ክሡተ። ኢያዕረፍከ፡ እምተናግሮ፡ ወኢረሰይከ፡ ሀኬተ።
                </incipit>
                <note>Concluded with a litany for the Nativity, <foreign xml:lang = "gez">ምልጣነ፤ ተወልደ፡ እምድንግል። ሰከበ፡ ውስተ፡ ጎል።</foreign><locus target = "#91r #91v"/></note>
                </msItem>
              <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.13"><locus from = "92r" to = "94v"/>
                <title>List of the sufferings of Jesus</title>
                <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                  ጸዋትወ፡ ሕማማት፡ ዘእግዚእነ፡ ወመድኀኒነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ዘዘበጥዎ፡ ገጾ፡...
                </incipit>
                </msItem>
              <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.14"><locus from = "94v" to = "95r"/>
                <title>Sälam to Täklä Haymanot, takne from the <foreign xml:lang = "gez">እግዚአብሔር፡ ነግሠ፡</foreign>, ascribed to <persName ref = "PRS10626ZaraY"/></title>
                <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                  ሰላም፡ ለተክለ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ናሕርየ፡ ወንጌል፡ ወወኦሪት። እምአመ፡ ተወልደ፡ ሰአት። ለእግዚአብሔር፡ ባረኮ፡ በሰላስ፡ ዕለት።
                </incipit>
                </msItem>
              <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.15"><locus from = "95v" to = "95r"/><title type = "complete" ref = "LIT2860RepCh141"/>
                <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                  ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምከ፡ ኀበ፡ ዓምደ፡ ወርቅ፡ ዘተጽሕገ። ምስለ፡ አበው፡ ኄራን፡ እንዘ፡ ይከውን፡ ሱቱፈ።
                </incipit>
                </msItem>
              <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.16"><locus from = "95v" to = "102r"/><title type = "complete" ref = "LIT2930RepCh211"/>
                <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                  ሰላም፡ ለጽንሰትከ፡ ወለልደትከ፡ እምከርሥ። አመ፡ ፳ወረቡዑ፡ ለወርኃ፡ ታኅሣሥ።
                </incipit>
                </msItem>
              <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.17"><locus from = "104r" to = "126v"/>
                <title>Image of the Trinity, <foreign xml:lang = "gez">መልክዐ፡ ሥላሴ፡</foreign></title>
                <note>Composed probably by a certain <foreign xml:lang = "gez">ታቦር፡</foreign> after <foreign xml:lang = "gez">ኢያሱ፡</foreign> (1682–1706) built the <foreign xml:lang = "gez">ደብረ፡ ብርሃነ፡ ሥላሴ፡</foreign> church in Gondär, cf. <locus target = "#127r #129r"/></note>
                <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                  ሰላም፡ ለሕጽንክሙ፡ ምርፋቀ፡ ጻድቃን፡ አግብርቲሁ። ማያተ፡ ኢያሱ፡ ሥላሴ፡ እለ፡ ትውሕዙ፡ እምሕሊናሁ።
                </incipit>
                </msItem>
              <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.18"><locus from = "127r" to = "129r"/>
                <title>Sälam, to <foreign xml:lang = "gez">አቡነፍር፡</foreign>, of <foreign xml:lang = "gez">ሰኔ፡ ፲፮፡</foreign></title>
                <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                  ስላም፡ ለአቡናር፡ ጊዜ፡ ተዳደቆ፡ መዊጥ። እንተ፡ ተወለጠ፡ ግጹ፡ አምሳለ፡ እሳጥ።
                </incipit>
                </msItem>
              <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.19"><locus from = "129r" />
                <title><term key = "Asmat"/> prayer against rinderpest (<foreign xml:lang = "gez">ኅኮር፡ (?)</foreign>). </title>
                <note>The Greek names of the nails of the cross are copied on <locus target = "#130v"/></note>
                <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                  አስማት፡ በእንተ፡ እንስሳ፡ ወበእንተ፡ አባግዕ፡ ወበእንተ፡ አጣሌ፡ ወኵሉ፡ ንዋየ፡ ሰብእ፡ ከመ፡ ኢይንድፋ፡  ለዓራዊት፡ ኅኮር፡ በኀጸ፡ ቀጢን፡...
                </incipit>
                </msItem>
              <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.20"><locus from = "129v" to = "131r"/><title type = "complete" ref = "LIT2765RepCh49"/>
                <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                  ሰላም፡ ለከ፡ ሰዳዴ፡ ሰዳዴ፡ አጋንንት፡ ፋኑኤል፡ ለእግዚብሔር፡ እምጽርሑ። ከመ፡ ኢይስክዩ፡ ሰብአ፡ እነ፡ ኢነስሑ።
                </incipit>
                </msItem>
              <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.21"><locus from = "134v" to = "138r"/><title type = "complete" ref = "LIT1190Baenta"/></msItem>
              <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.22"><locus from = "138v" to = "140r"/>
                <title>What seems to be a hymn/song praising what <foreign xml:lang = "gez">ኢዮአስ፡</foreign> (1747–1761) has done for the monastery of Abunä Täklä Haymanot</title>
                <note>Supplied with musical notation, insufficiently legible</note>
                </msItem>
              </msItem>

